body_html: Example Tensorflow convolutional code (e.g. https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/master/tensorflow/models/image/mnist/convolutional.py) does not run with the binary installed version and instead apparently requires buildng from source. See #1235. How do we build from source given this issue?

body: Example Tensorflow convolutional code (e.g. https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/master/tensorflow/models/image/mnist/convolutional.py) does not run with the binary installed version and instead apparently requires buildng from source.
